values: You are reading the multipleshots@livejournal.com... or not. Strictly friends only; have a good day.

Just have a little patience
 I'm still hurting from a love I lost
 I'm feeling your frustration
 Any minute all the pain will stop.
 
 Just hold me close inside your arms tonight
 Don't be too hard on my emotions.

 'Cause I
 Need time
 My heart is numb, has no feeling
 So while I'm still healing
 Just try and have a little patience.

And then when you feel like the whole world's just crashing down on your shoulders, and you don't have anything to live for,

the cold hard facts of life become clear to you that you're actually right.

You don't have anything to live for.

So what of life?
What of all this endless misery and pure torture?

Change

Seems like nothing is black and white anymore
Shades of grey and I feel a weight over my shoulder
It's tough getting older
I always thought that I knew where I'd want to go
Now I'm here and I find that I'm still getting colder
It's kinda tough getting older

Here before my eyes, many roads ahead
Time for me to choose one way now
If I take a chance
What lies down the road
Feeling so confused, turned round
On and on, on and on
yeah yeah.....
